ygData.messageBody:
I'll volunteer to watch over the Veeshan server. I already have a few str8 friends that want to join. I told them how great you guys are and I read we don't discriminate so I hope its ok. I have been on Veeshan since Public release and I have been playing EQ since early November. I have also been a lead officer in one other guild before on this server and just to warn, there are 2 reasons I will auto-eject a member from a guild, Severe Harrasement and constant begging after warned (ie, someone give me something for free, yadda yadda). The reason I left this guild will be explained in my next email.


Tiger =)
